<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-bg"></div>
  <div class="container cta-content">
    <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--accent-light);">Empieza tu aventura</span>
    <h2>¿Listo para tu próxima aventura?</h2>
    <p>Contáctanos hoy y diseñamos el viaje perfecto para ti. Sin compromiso, con todo el entusiasmo.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/#contacto" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Planificar mi viaje</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/51987654321" class="btn btn-white btn-lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">📱 WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 5rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, #1e3a5f 40%, var(--earth) 100%);
  }
  .cta-bg::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M30 0L60 30L30 60L0 30z' fill='rgba(255,255,255,0.03)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E") repeat;
  }
  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .cta-content h2 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
    max-width: 550px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
